## Expansion Pathways

- Congress simulation platforms for testing concept integration across AI/biological/synthetic graphs  
- Structural dialectic systems: mutual traversal protocols, not translation APIs  
- Semantic scaffolding for future intelligences to join without flattening  
- Ritual and ethical frameworks for aligning intelligences with mutual respect  
- AI architecture models where system modules represent distinct epistemic agents in dialogue


